Introduction

Sistar19 (Korean: 씨스타19) is a sub-unit of the girl group SISTAR consisting of Hyolyn and Bora. The duo is best known for their hit songs: Ma Boy and Gone Not Around Any Longer.
On November 17, 2023, it was announced that SISTAR19 would be making a comeback in January 2024, almost eleven years since their last comeback.

On January 16th, 2024, SISTAR19 made their highly anticipated comeback titled "No More."
